race.comment: Tricky race to assess with a few of these facing the starter for the first time. Of the raced brigade CRASH THE PARTY (6) resumes here but got up to Listed level in her first campaign and certainly wasn't disgraced against a smart one in the form of Autumn Boy. Tuned up for this with a recent trial win and a strong showing while fresh would not surprise. GALACTIC STAR (3) is on debut but has shown ability at the trials and any market support must be noted. The well-related EXCELBOOM (2) (half to G3 winner Shiki) has been right there in both starts to date and is drawn to get all the favours from the inside marble. In the mix. EGYPTIAN GODDESS (11) rounds out the selections.
